List of non-profit Organizations
The most efficient and effective way to help the Afghan people is to make a monetary donation to a humanitarian organization that is currently implementing aid programs in Afghanistan.
Monetary donations allow humanitarian organizations to purchase (often in Afghanistan itself or nearby) the exact type and quantity of items needed by the Afghan people.
To learn more about why, please visit our page on effective giving.
To donate, click below to visit an organizations website:
